{"tid":762302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國前AV女Mia Khalifa被冰球擊中打爆假胸","createTime":"2018-07-31T07:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T21:11:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":449,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"2577d7785d07bc3ac07365b2b761d42dc68f2c07","tid":762302,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180730/large/1532947024_1a70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180730%2Flarge%2F1532947024_1a70.jpg&h=b08e936b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n25歲美國前色情片女星Mia Khalifa月前睇冰上曲棍球賽事時，不幸被冰球擊中左胸，令其左邊乳房植入物破裂，佢已計劃明年胸部再動手術。<br />\n<br />\nMia憶述當時於無防避之下被打中：「我當時即抓住我的胸部，不想放手，因為覺得一放手就會到處都是血。冰球好重，速度達至80mph，我覺得我的左邊胸部扁了，我會明年再動手術。」不過作為球迷嘅佢，覺得呢個都唔算係一個好差嘅經歷，Mia話將個冰球拎咗番屋企做紀念：「一個曾打中你的冰球，會是任何球迷的最正紀念品。」"},{"pid":"aef94889d935c28dc0c8070ff411fc9ce7b647ea","tid":762302,"uid":84668,"like":502,"dislike":5,"score":497,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"整返對真啲架啦<br />\n<br />\n太假J唔落"},{"pid":"1b9461e2137c2bef43e90a8617122d5d7b6d929f","tid":762302,"uid":55914,"like":641,"dislike":2,"score":639,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"冇個假胸擋一擋係咪會打死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96afc49e3d828c06379047564b52559aec3bad74","tid":762302,"uid":163743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"慘慘豬"},{"pid":"c06405bac8a53bdd981c110cd64b2cf32d98182a","tid":762302,"uid":2772,"like":330,"dislike":11,"score":319,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"講到咁撚鍾意<br />\n直頭整埋粒冰球做LIN餅丫笨"},{"pid":"dcb54b33b00b6397b9cfe4e96df3e1392679c1e1","tid":762302,"uid":33352,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"唔係有有玻璃擋住咩"},{"pid":"3027ba2378184ac88fa9cac75c95264cd3782b22","tid":762302,"uid":45393,"like":672,"dislike":4,"score"